quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  22,73,"You, you the people, (an) example/proverb was given , so listen to it, that those whom you call from other than God they will never/not create a fly/insanity and even if they gathered/unified/combined for it, and if the fly/insanity ravishes/robs them forcefully (of) a thing, they will not rescue/save it from it, the seeker/wanter and the sought after/wanted were weakened"
  22,74,"They did not evaluate/estimate God His deserved/true value/estimation/capability , that truly God (is) powerful/strong (E), glorious/mighty"
  22,75,"God chooses/purifies from the angels messengers, and from the people, that truly God (is) hearing/listening, seeing/understanding"
  22,76,"He knows what (is) between their hands, and what (is) behind them, and to God the matters/affairs are returned"
  22,77,"You, you those who believed, bow , and prostrate, and worship your Lord, and make/do the good ,maybe/perhaps you succeed/win"
  22,78,"And struggle/do (your) utmost His deserved/true struggle , He chose/purified you, and He did not make/put on you in the religion from strain/hardship , your father Abraham`s religion/faith, He named/identified you the Moslems/submitters/surrenderers from before, and in this the Messenger to be a witness/present on you, and you be witnessing/testifying/witnesses/testifiers on the people, so stand/keep up the prayers, and give/bring the charity/ purification , and hold fast/take shelter with/by God, He is your master/ally , so blessed/praised (is) the master/ally , and blessed/praised (is) the victorior/savior"